summary: A small Mod I made for my class.
descriptionHtml:
Now is the time for a story to tell,about a wish from a king, that didn't go well.But for the queen, a pleasant surprise,something to do, from sunset to sunrise.

This is a mod that I made for my college painting class. Our job was to create something that had contrasting elements (High society vs Low). So I came into class with this! Please let me know what you think, and how you think I could have improved.Â 

Have a look a my picture to know where to start!

P.S. If you want more, have a look where you would least expect..... lets just say, you never knew that being a companion was so...... hard.
author: Bradzy
